properties.name: fill-color
properties.description: Color which will be filled into circle.

properties.name: fill-opacity
properties.description: Opacity of color which is filled into circle.

properties.name: stroke-color
properties.description: Color which is filled into stroke

properties.name: visible
properties.description: Whether circle is visible or not.

properties.name: z-index
properties.description: Z index of circle on map.

events.name: double-click
events.description: Raised when circle is doubly clicked.

events.name: right-click
events.description: Raised when circle is right clicked.

events.name: mouse-over
events.description: Raised when mouse moves over the circle (without being pressed down)

events.name: mouse-out
events.description: Raised when mouse moves out of circle

events.name: mouse-down
events.description: Raised when mouse is pressed down on circle.

events.name: mouse-up
events.description: Raised when mouse is released from circle.

events.name: bounds-changed
events.description: Raised when circle bounds are changed.
